channel.title: Raised a PR after making changes in code of data source, but “percy/redash — 1 visual change needs review” check was not successful. Need help regarding this
channel.description:
Hi Team,
I have raised a [PR ](https://github.com/getredash/redash/pull/5689) after making changes in code of data source Firebolt. CI was ran and I got this one error “percy/redash — 1 visual change needs review”. When I checked files produced by getredash:master and rajeshmauryasde:firebolt-integration2, there was no visual difference I could find. Please let me know how may I proceed further to get this resolved. [Failed case link ](https://percy.io/Redash/redash/builds/15193044/changed/858388015?browser=chrome&browser_ids=20&subcategories=unreviewed%2Cchanges_requested&viewLayout=overlay&viewMode=new&width=1280&widths=375%2C1280)
Thank you.

We’re working to straighten out the Percy issue. It’s not related to your change. Just something messy in our infrastructure. Thanks for calling attention to it.
